messageBody:
Hi everyone,

I am a Graduate student at the University of Manchester in the United
Kingdom. I am currently undertaking a dissertation project on the
operation of Wikis within private organisations and enterprises as
well as within a public domain. I am inviting your assistance by
soliciting your participation in this survey. In this survey, you will
be asked questions about issues of vandalism, maintenance, and edit
wars as they relate to the functioning of the Wiki. The Questionnaire
consists of 18 questions and will take at most 10 minutes to complete.

Here is the survey link:
http://www.surveyconsole.com/console/TakeSurvey?id=362152

Thank all of you in advance,
